description: A sunlit 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home awaits through a private entrance, offering over 1700 sq ft of living space spread across 3 stories. The second floor features a high-end kitchen with Thermador stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, white cabinetry, a beautiful tile backsplash, and a spacious center island. Entertaining is a breeze with a deck off the dining area. Upstairs, the lavish primary suite awaits, along with two other oversized bedrooms and a centrally located bathroom. The head-house provides easy access to the private roof deck, while the property also includes 2 full-size side-by-side parking spaces, hardwood floors throughout, in-unit W/D, AC. Located less than one block away from South Boston's highly coveted Carson Beach and just a short distance from the vibrant East Broadway area.
